  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Jukebox
    Manages 3 objects of type Queue of SongEntry - favoritePL, roadTripPL and loungePL favoritePL simulates playlist referred as "favorites" in input file, roadTripPL simulates playlist referred to as "road trip" in input file, loungePL simulates playlist referred to as "lounge" in input file An instance of the class reads a file which includes the user's requests for a the name of a song to be added to a specific playlist.
